     5‚Üí## Usage
     6‚Üí
     7‚ÜíTo start using the library, install it in your project:
     8‚Üí
     9‚Üí```bash
    10‚Üínpm install sonner
    11‚Üí```
    12‚Üí
    13‚ÜíAdd `<Toaster />` to your app, it will be the place where all your toasts will be rendered.
    14‚ÜíAfter that you can use `toast()` from anywhere in your app.
    15‚Üí
    16‚Üí```jsx
    17‚Üíimport { Toaster, toast } from 'sonner';
    18‚Üí
    19‚Üí// ...
    20‚Üí
    21‚Üífunction App() {
    22‚Üí  return (
    23‚Üí    <div>
    24‚Üí      <Toaster />
    25‚Üí      <button onClick={() => toast('My first toast')}>Give me a toast</button>
    26‚Üí    </div>
    27‚Üí  );
    28‚Üí}
    29‚Üí```
    30‚Üí
    31‚Üí## Documentation
    32‚Üí
    33‚ÜíFind the full API reference in the [documentation](https://sonner.emilkowal.ski/getting-started).
